Kei-chan's so cute! She keeps flashing me
those puppy-dog eyes only kids can do.

rows.label: tlk70000050_05_msg0002
rows.name:
I wonder if she's on to my secret snack
stash...?

rows.label: tlk70000050_05_msg0003
rows.name:
I mean, I wonder if she thinks I have a
secret snack stash! Which of course I
don't! Ahahahahaha!

rows.label: tlk70000050_05_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe she'll keep quiet about it if I
share some of my snacks with her...
